00:21:10,479 --> 00:21:13,315
lf you want, you can
come down here and hang out...

336
00:21:13,398 --> 00:21:15,442
Nobody talk.

337
00:21:15,526 --> 00:21:18,070
Just drink.

338
00:21:19,112 --> 00:21:22,282
<i>Uncomfortable silences
